{"tid":1633443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［勇武入］8日之後《美國人權法案》將會通過","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:56:02.000Z","uid":12244,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e0270f9937ef551be4aecc2020582bb782f5160a","tid":1633443,"uid":12244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:04:04.000Z","msg":"勇武做法絕對無錯，但認為宜家要打返慢小小<br />\n<br />\n宜家好似個節奏比人掌控住咁，人地做咩都好，我地淨係識打反擊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想大家比少少時間《美國人權法案》過左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，呢兩日黑警態度係差同挑釁，但除左便衣開實彈果下，但係鏡頭下用暴力嘅情況係少左。<br />\n<br />\n建議今晚大可以係商場唱下歌，之後大家鍾意嘅可以快閃堵路，法案一過先升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還掂啲舖都裝修到咁上下，比佢地執返好，之後大把時間玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲中資銀行就唔好搞住，睇下聽日多唔多人排隊攞錢，同埋法案過唔過到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果法案其實係過唔撚到，全力支持勇武無上限武力升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7152f819a05cbe7b8d32eb8167579c381f800c","tid":1633443,"uid":12244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"推比勇武手足見到"},{"pid":"19754b883c9f396472fa8b9914d41a500d9ad6ea","tid":1633443,"uid":273576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:05:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d6e48e45e37816a05c92491e8c026c3de25ddf","tid":1633443,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"邊到話8日後過？"},{"pid":"9d8107ccac5072bd382f02b9cb42ed7b6cc36c16","tid":1633443,"uid":294173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:06:17.000Z","